\/03\/28131453\/low-platform-bed-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A platform bed is always low-raised!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Platform Bed With Storage&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Platform bed designs with storage don&#8217;t just look good; they are super functional. Many of us are constantly working towards keeping our bedroom clutter-free. Where to keep all the stuff? <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/storage-bed-design\/\">Traditional bed storage<\/a> can be a hassle in daily use. With platform beds, you can opt for built-in storage, which can be in the form of shelves, pull-out drawers, and under-bed storage for clothing, bedding, and other household items.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131446\/platform-bed-designs-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Platform bed with storage which is super functional\" class=\"wp-image-55223\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131446\/platform-bed-designs-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131446\/platform-bed-designs-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131446\/platform-bed-designs-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131446\/platform-bed-designs-with-storage-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131446\/platform-bed-designs-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Get more storage with your bed<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Platform Bed Frame Designs&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are so many different platform bed frame design plans available. A classic one is a &#8216;raised&#8217; or &#8216;elevated&#8217; bed frame. This design choice creates a sense of openness and adds a visual lightness to the bed, unlike frames that rest directly on the floor. This style is popular for its minimalist aesthetic, allowing for easy cleaning underneath. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe expert designers<\/a> can help you design your dream <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom interiors<\/a> with a guaranteed 20% extra space!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131438\/platform-bed-frame-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Platform bed frame design in green colour for a minimalistic look\" class=\"wp-image-55222\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131438\/platform-bed-frame-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131438\/platform-bed-frame-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131438\/platform-bed-frame-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131438\/platform-bed-frame-designs-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131438\/platform-bed-frame-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">This green bed is a showstopper<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Platform Bed: Sharp &amp; Stylish<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Modern platform beds follow a minimalist approach. The design features a low-profile, rectangular or box-like structure, often with clean lines and a sleek appearance. Like us, if you believe in a simple yet sophisticated-looking room that is clutter-free, comfortable, and modern, investing in a modern platform bed would be the right call.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out trending bedroom interiors of 2024 here:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedroom-design-trends-2024\/\">https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedroom-design-trends-2024\/<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131430\/modern-platform-bed-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Modern platform bed design which is minimalistic in approach\" class=\"wp-image-55221\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131430\/modern-platform-bed-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131430\/modern-platform-bed-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131430\/modern-platform-bed-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131430\/modern-platform-bed-designs-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131430\/modern-platform-bed-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A minimalist design complements the simple interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Explore trendy bedroom designs with ample storage solutions\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/09143050\/explore-trendy-bedroom-designs-with-ample-storage-solutions.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Platform Bed Ideas for Small Room<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For a compact room, platform beds offer a clever choice where the need is for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/space-saving-furniture-small-indian-homes\/\">space-saving furniture<\/a> and a &#8216;less is more&#8217; approach. A platform bed&#8217;s low height, smooth finish, and flat structure can enhance the spaciousness of a bedroom. You can have a beautiful bedroom with some neutral colours on the walls. For a kid&#8217;s room, you can safely opt for this design that offers storage, convenience, comfort, and safety for little toddlers to move around.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131414\/platform-bed-designs-for-small-rooms.jpg\" alt=\"Platform bed design ideas for a small room which maximises space\" class=\"wp-image-55219\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131414\/platform-bed-designs-for-small-rooms.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131414\/platform-bed-designs-for-small-rooms-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131414\/platform-bed-designs-for-small-rooms-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131414\/platform-bed-designs-for-small-rooms-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131414\/platform-bed-designs-for-small-rooms-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Maximise space without additional furniture<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wood Platform Bed&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>While platform beds are stylish- you also have the option of designing your platform bed in solid, raw wood. Solid wood platform beds are carved entirely from raw wood to retain their natural texture and feel. Naturally expensive, these beds provide durability, sturdiness, and a timeless appeal, making them popular in contemporary, modern, and vintage platform bed interior design styles.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131405\/solid-wood-platform-bed-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden platform design which has a natural texture and looks stylish\" class=\"wp-image-55218\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131405\/solid-wood-platform-bed-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131405\/solid-wood-platform-bed-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131405\/solid-wood-platform-bed-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131405\/solid-wood-platform-bed-designs-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131405\/solid-wood-platform-bed-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Immerse yourself in the earthiness of a solid wood bed<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contemporary Platform Bed Design&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To take things up a notch, for those seeking an eclectic and unique bed design, the contemporary platform bed is the perfect choice. We are talking about a blend of design elements, including opting for different materials such as wood, metal, and textured frames through upholstery and some innovative features to stand out. This bed style offers an artistic appeal to your bedroom and is sure to attract guest compliments.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131421\/contemporary-platform-bed-designs.jpg\" alt=\"Contemporary platform bed design which looks eclectic and unique\" class=\"wp-image-55220\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131421\/contemporary-platform-bed-designs.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131421\/contemporary-platform-bed-designs-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131421\/contemporary-platform-bed-designs-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131421\/contemporary-platform-bed-designs-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/28131421\/contemporary-platform-bed-designs-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The no-nonsense bed frame is right out of designer books<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Due to their &#8216;long-lasting&#8217; furniture trait, beds are an investment. Choosing a well-designed and sturdy bed frame that lives longer, looks good, and offers the same comfort is important. Platform beds are a popular trend this year. The buyers are spoilt for choices with a pool of options and customisation available. Most importantly, these beds tick the budget criteria while being stylish, resulting in high demand in the market.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for more than just a bed?<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\"> Explore DesignCafe&#8217;s complete home interiors<\/a>, which come with up to a 20-year warranty, ensuring your dream home interiors are stylish and sturdy!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">Book A FREE Consultation<\/a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Platform Beds<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Are platform beds easy to assemble?<\/strong><br>Yes, platform beds are generally easy to assemble. Depending on the type of platform bed chosen, you can easily assemble all its parts, such as the base and headboard, using basic tools. However, it&#8217;s advised to consult the manufacturer and refer to the guidebook.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What materials are commonly used in platform bed designs?<\/strong><br>Commonly used materials in platform bed designs include wood, metal, and upholstered fabrics. Wooden beds offer a vintage look, metal beds are commonly used in contemporary design, and upholstered fabrics can give a luxurious touch to the bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Do platform beds provide adequate support for heavier individuals?<\/strong><br>Platform beds can provide adequate support for heavier individuals. With proper construction, support structure, and quality materials, you can safely rely on platform beds. For added comfort, you can choose a flat platform bed frame.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Can I use a platform bed with an adjustable mattress?<\/strong><br>Yes, platform beds are compatible with adjustable mattresses. The platform bed should have features like flexible slats or an adjustable solid base for a comfortable and hassle-free experience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Are there platform bed designs suitable for small spaces?<\/strong><br>Yes. The platform bed designs are perfect for small spaces. Featuring a low-raised platform, ample built-in storage options, and a sleek finish, they promote a space-saving, clutter-free, and spacious environment, ideal for compact bedrooms.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-grou